snippet.title: The Painscreek Killings   Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam store page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/624270/The_Painscreek_Killings/
Website: http://painscreekkillings.com/
The Painscreek Killings is a first-person, explorable mystery solving game set in a fictional town of United States in the 1990s. As Janet, a young and upcoming journalist, you are to uncover the secrets behind the town killings and publish the truth in the city papers.
#ThePainscreekKillings
